      'https://picsum.photos/id/40/800/600',
      'https://picsum.photos/id/41/800/600',
      'https://picsum.photos/id/42/800/600'
    ],
    description: `
      <h3>User Research Phase</h3>
      <p>Conducted extensive user research including 50+ user interviews, usability testing sessions, and competitive analysis. Identified key pain points that were causing 30% user drop-off rates.</p>

