      <p>Developed a comprehensive design system and user journey maps. Implemented accessibility standards (WCAG 2.1 AA) and created responsive designs that work seamlessly across all devices.</p>

      <h3>Implementation Results</h3>
      <p>The redesign resulted in a 45% increase in user engagement, 60% reduction in support tickets, and 25% improvement in conversion rates. Users reported 80% higher satisfaction scores.</p>

      <h3>Design Deliverables</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>User personas and journey maps</li>
        <li>Wireframes and prototypes</li>
        <li>Design system documentation</li>
        <li>Accessibility audit reports</li>
        <li>Usability testing results</li>
      </ul>
    `,
    tech: ['Figma', 'Adobe XD', 'InVision', 'Maze', 'Google Analytics'],
    duration: '8 months',
