      <p>Developed a hybrid recommendation system combining collaborative filtering, content-based filtering, and deep learning models. Implemented real-time A/B testing and continuous model retraining.</p>

      <h3>Technical Architecture</h3>
      <p>Built using TensorFlow and deployed on AWS SageMaker. The system processes 10 million+ user interactions daily, providing personalized recommendations with 85% accuracy.</p>

      <h3>Business Impact</h3>
